110
00:08:48.319 --> 00:08:50.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Barge 12 is that way. Tier 2.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:51.364 --> 00:08:53.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Xanthan marmot chirping )</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:09:01.290 --> 00:09:03.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:09:04.669 --> 00:09:06.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm closed.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:09:07.505 --> 00:09:08.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have an appointment.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:09:12.218 --> 00:09:14.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We met at the deuterium station</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on Norellus.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:15.388 --> 00:09:17.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll have to come back later.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:17.890 --> 00:09:22.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said you could sell us the formula</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to synthesize trellium-D.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:23.062 --> 00:09:25.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you didn't bring us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all this way for nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:26.482 --> 00:09:29.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Archer. I remember now.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:29.694 --> 00:09:30.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:31.404 --> 00:09:34.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A little pressed for time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:35.449 --> 00:09:40.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trellium-A is extremely common,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>easy to synthesize,</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:40.413 --> 00:09:45.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but trellium-D is rare,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>difficult to process.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:45.835 --> 00:09:47.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And expensive?</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:48.129 --> 00:09:51.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm confident we can agree</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on a fair price.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:52.633 --> 00:09:54.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was thinking about you recently,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:54.844 --> 00:09:58.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were very eager to learn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Xindi, as I recall.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:58.431 --> 00:10:01.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is your interest in them?</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:10:02.351 --> 00:10:04.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're on a diplomatic mission.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:10:04.395 --> 00:10:06.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A diplomatic mission.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:06.772 --> 00:10:08.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:08.107 --> 00:10:11.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some Xindi arrived here last week.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:11.611 --> 00:10:13.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you might be interested.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:13.946 --> 00:10:15.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where can we find them?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:15.364 --> 00:10:17.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They had business with another merchant.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:17.742 --> 00:10:19.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who?</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:22.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be happy to direct you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a small fee.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:25.041 --> 00:10:28.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Tucker has the list</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of supplies and equipment</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:28.794 --> 00:10:30.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we'd be willing to barter.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:30.171 --> 00:10:31.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a gesture of good faith,</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:32.006 --> 00:10:34.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>why don't you tell me where</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can find this merchant,</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:38.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then you and Mr. Tucker</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can work out the details.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:38.304 --> 00:10:42.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm confident we can agree</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on a fair price.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:42.808 --> 00:10:45.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( aliens chattering )</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:48.314 --> 00:10:50.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>FEMALE: Do you like what you see?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:01.243 --> 00:11:07.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To answer your first question,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I regret I cannot offer free samples.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:11:07.792 --> 00:11:10.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Rat Ud said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you might be able to help us.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:12.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I always welcome referrals.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:14.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is your pleasure?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:14.632 --> 00:11:17.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were told you've recently</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>done business with some Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:19.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excellent customers.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:20.137 --> 00:11:23.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They purchased two U'tani serpent women.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:23.557 --> 00:11:25.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid I don't have any more,</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:25.184 --> 00:11:29.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but perhaps I could interest you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a nuvian concubine.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:30.356 --> 00:11:33.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's quite skilled.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:34.860 --> 00:11:36.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not interested.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:37.405 --> 00:11:40.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where I can find these Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:40.533 --> 00:11:43.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe they left orbit two days ago.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:44.745 --> 00:11:46.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where were they heading?</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:46.330 --> 00:11:48.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't stay in business for very long</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:48.666 --> 00:11:51.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if I revealed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>confidential information about my clients.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:52.503 --> 00:11:55.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have females here from many worlds.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:56.090 --> 00:11:57.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who knows?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:58.551 --> 00:12:03.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps one of them can tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you want to know about the Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:26.454 --> 00:12:29.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have an excellent eye, my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:30.541 --> 00:12:33.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She can be very accommodating.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:36.922 --> 00:12:38.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:41.010 --> 00:12:42.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:42.219 --> 00:12:44.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain, B'Rat and I</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>have agreed on a price.</i></c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:44.513 --> 00:12:46.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll need to go back</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the ship for his payment.</i></c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:46.765 --> 00:12:49.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Understood. We'll meet you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back at the shuttlepod.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:50.769 --> 00:12:53.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can you walk away from such beauty?</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:58.319 --> 00:12:59.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks for your time.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:13:06.702 --> 00:13:10.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After an hour in this place,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can't wait to get back to decon.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:13:13.292 --> 00:13:15.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( crashing )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALE: Stop her!</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:23.135 --> 00:13:24.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE 2: Watch yourself!</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:27.306 --> 00:13:29.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take me with you, please!</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:29.183 --> 00:13:30.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:30.935 --> 00:13:32.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She seems determined to be sold today.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:33.395 --> 00:13:35.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go back to my shop</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and arrange for payment.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:13:37.233 --> 00:13:38.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think so.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:13:38.943 --> 00:13:40.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I'll take my merchandise.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:41.028 --> 00:13:43.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like she doesn't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go with you.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:43.697 --> 00:13:46.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're so concerned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about what she wants, buy her.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:46.784 --> 00:13:49.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Otherwise, stay out of my business!</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:57.169 --> 00:13:59.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:14:24.196 --> 00:14:27.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Let's get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Gladly.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:14:40.504 --> 00:14:42.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have the most intriguing eyes.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:14:44.091 --> 00:14:46.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never seen a retinal structure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this complex.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:14:47.011 --> 00:14:48.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:14:51.932 --> 00:14:53.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How's our guest?</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:14:53.517 --> 00:14:55.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not familiar with her species</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:14:55.394 --> 00:14:58.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, uh, she appears to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in perfect health.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:07.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid I don't even know your name.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:15:09.825 --> 00:15:11.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm called Rajiin.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:15.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very grateful for what</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've done, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:15:15.664 --> 00:15:17.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll serve you well, I promise.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:15:20.669 --> 00:15:22.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get something straight.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:15:24.298 --> 00:15:27.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't believe one person</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can own another person.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:30.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're free to go wherever you'd like.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:15:32.389 --> 00:15:34.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How far is your homeworld?</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:15:34.892 --> 00:15:36.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:15:36.852 --> 00:15:38.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm told it's called Oran'taku,</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:15:38.729 --> 00:15:41.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I don't remember it.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:15:42.691 --> 00:15:45.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Do you have any family?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've had many owners.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:15:49.031 --> 00:15:52.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have some data on this region of space.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:15:52.201 --> 00:15:56.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see if I can locate Oran'taku.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:15:56.622 --> 00:15:58.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it's possible, we'll take you there.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:15:59.166 --> 00:16:01.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Set her up in quarters.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get her whatever she needs.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:16:01.377 --> 00:16:02.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:16:02.378 --> 00:16:03.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:16:05.673 --> 00:16:06.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:16:13.722 --> 00:16:15.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On our planet,</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:16:16.767 --> 00:16:19.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>wars were fought over these.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:16:19.395 --> 00:16:21.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:16:21.146 --> 00:16:23.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:16:27.403 --> 00:16:29.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Careful.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:16:29.905 --> 00:16:32.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snorting )</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:16:33.492 --> 00:16:35.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sneezes )</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:16:36.453 --> 00:16:38.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:16:38.414 --> 00:16:39.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's this one called?</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:16:39.915 --> 00:16:41.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Black pepper.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Ooh!</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:16:41.750 --> 00:16:44.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's paprika, mustard seed.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:16:44.211 --> 00:16:46.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm partial to the cayenne myself.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:16:46.130 --> 00:16:49.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure you'll find these all</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>very exotic.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:16:49.550 --> 00:16:51.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe you have something for us?</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:16:52.011 --> 00:16:53.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:16:55.139 --> 00:16:59.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've reviewed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your engineering specifications.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:16:59.351 --> 00:17:04.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You appear to have the necessary equipment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to produce liquid trellium-D.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:17:04.314 --> 00:17:05.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Liquid?</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:17:05.524 --> 00:17:09.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trellium can only be synthesized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a liquid state.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:17:09.778 --> 00:17:13.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just as effective as the natural ore.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:17:13.240 --> 00:17:15.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then all we need is the recipe.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:17:15.159 --> 00:17:17.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, there is one thing.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:17:18.704 --> 00:17:22.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be sure to follow the protocols precisely.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:17:23.792 --> 00:17:25.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or?</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:17:25.085 --> 00:17:28.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's just say that in its liquid form,</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:17:28.922 --> 00:17:33.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>trellium-D is extremely unstable.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:17:40.517 --> 00:17:43.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Zjod snorting, sneezing )</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:17:43.312 --> 00:17:45.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:17:46.273 --> 00:17:47.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ooh!</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:17:57.284 --> 00:17:59.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are your accommodations?</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:18:00.412 --> 00:18:02.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Much better than I'm used to.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:18:03.373 --> 00:18:06.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last ship I was on,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I never left the cargo hold.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:07.419 --> 00:18:10.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Except for a few visits</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the captain's quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:14.301 --> 00:18:17.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are some restricted areas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:18.263 --> 00:18:20.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Otherwise, feel free to look around.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:18:21.100 --> 00:18:22.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your crew won't mind?</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:18:24.728 --> 00:18:26.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I seriously doubt it.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:28.941 --> 00:18:32.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are they all from Earth?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nearly all.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:18:32.111 --> 00:18:34.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You met Dr. Phlox. He's from Denobula.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:18:34.655 --> 00:18:36.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And my First Officer's a Vulcan.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:18:38.784 --> 00:18:42.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Phlox mentioned you were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on an important mission.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:18:42.830 --> 00:18:46.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're trying to make contact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a species called Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:18:46.125 --> 00:18:48.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't suppose you know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything about them?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:18:48.836 --> 00:18:50.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very little.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:51.004 --> 00:18:55.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The two I saw looked reptilian,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and they weren't very pleasant.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:55.926 --> 00:18:59.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At the time, I was just relieved</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they weren't interested in me.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:19:00.389 --> 00:19:01.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you looking for them?</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:02.808 --> 00:19:05.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're hoping to resolve a disagreement.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:05.769 --> 00:19:08.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( intercom beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Tucker to Captain Archer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:09.565 --> 00:19:10.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:12.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We're in business, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:12.985 --> 00:19:14.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be right there.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:15.904 --> 00:19:16.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:19.074 --> 00:19:20.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door closing )</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:21.326 --> 00:19:22.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: How unstable?</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:23.036 --> 00:19:25.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough to do some serious damage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we screw this up.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:25.873 --> 00:19:28.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And we're supposed to insulate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the entire ship with it?</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:28.584 --> 00:19:30.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's only volatile in its liquid form.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:30.419 --> 00:19:34.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once we apply it to the inner hull</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it sets, it's completely safe.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:36.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tricky part's cookin' it up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the first place.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:19:36.633 --> 00:19:38.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It'll require extremely precise</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>calculations,</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:19:38.886 --> 00:19:42.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I believe Mr. Tucker and I</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can synthesize the compound safely.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:19:43.182 --> 00:19:44.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get started.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:19:44.141 --> 00:19:46.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I recommend we set up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a lab on E-deck</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:19:46.143 --> 00:19:49.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>within the emergency bulkheads,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a precaution.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:19:56.820 --> 00:19:58.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighing )</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:19:59.489 --> 00:20:01.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:02.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:20:14.504 --> 00:20:16.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good evening, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:20:16.548 --> 00:20:17.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is everything all right?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:20:17.841 --> 00:20:19.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry to disturb you.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:20:19.593 --> 00:20:21.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hoped you might have time to talk.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:20:22.679 --> 00:20:24.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um...</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:20:24.264 --> 00:20:27.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm, uh, not quite, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:20:28.477 --> 00:20:29.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:20:36.276 --> 00:20:38.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant to speak with you earlier.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:20:38.153 --> 00:20:40.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have some good news.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:20:40.113 --> 00:20:44.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol was able to locate your home planet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a database we acquired.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:20:44.284 --> 00:20:45.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's only two days away.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:20:49.289 --> 00:20:51.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't seem very pleased.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:20:52.334 --> 00:20:55.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was taken away when I was very young.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:20:55.921 --> 00:20:59.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't remember much about it.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:20:59.132 --> 00:21:01.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I doubt anyone there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would remember me.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:21:03.428 --> 00:21:05.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never know.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:21:05.806 --> 00:21:08.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem very memorable to me.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:21:11.019 --> 00:21:13.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm very grateful for what you've done,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:21:16.024 --> 00:21:18.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to repay you for your kindness.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:21:19.319 --> 00:21:20.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That isn't necessary.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:21:21.071 --> 00:21:22.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:21:23.448 --> 00:21:24.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rajiin, you--</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:21:25.492 --> 00:21:28.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a reason I was taken from my home.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:21:29.496 --> 00:21:32.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have certain gifts.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:21:33.083 --> 00:21:35.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you like me to show you?</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:21:37.129 --> 00:21:42.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That... really isn't something that--</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:21:46.346 --> 00:21:48.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:21:51.727 --> 00:21:54.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( faint hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:22:22.716 --> 00:22:24.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:22:25.052 --> 00:22:26.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:22:28.346 --> 00:22:29.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:22:30.807 --> 00:22:33.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I just wanted to say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>thank you again.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:22:35.437 --> 00:22:37.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be leaving orbit soon.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:22:39.149 --> 00:22:40.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good night.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:22:40.317 --> 00:22:41.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:22:41.526 --> 00:22:43.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good night.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:22:54.706 --> 00:22:56.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the molecular pressure?</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:22:56.124 --> 00:22:57.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Up to 1,100 units.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:22:57.918 --> 00:22:59.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Boy, this stuff is tricky.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:22:59.252 --> 00:23:00.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:23:00.921 --> 00:23:04.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decrease the theta bombardment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by 6%... No, 7%.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:23:06.551 --> 00:23:09.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pressure's still rising, 1,400 units.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:23:09.763 --> 00:23:11.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>1,430.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:23:11.515 --> 00:23:13.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Damn it! ( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:23:13.683 --> 00:23:15.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill the theta radiation altogether.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:23:15.977 --> 00:23:17.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping continues )</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:23:18.647 --> 00:23:19.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No effect.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:23:20.398 --> 00:23:22.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should seal off this section and leave.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:23:22.901 --> 00:23:25.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A sustained burst of delta radiation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>might do the trick.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:23:25.487 --> 00:23:27.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it might not. We should evacuate.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:23:27.864 --> 00:23:30.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to ramp the delta to 80%.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:23:32.744 --> 00:23:33.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not working.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:23:34.079 --> 00:23:35.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're welcome to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:23:35.664 --> 00:23:37.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pressure is up to 2,000 units.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:23:37.374 --> 00:23:39.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( warning alarm beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Commander!</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:23:50.303 --> 00:23:51.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughs )</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:23:55.267 --> 00:23:58.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some of our calculations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>may have been slightly off.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:23:58.895 --> 00:24:00.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're back to square one.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:24:02.399 --> 00:24:03.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:24:04.025 --> 00:24:05.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been working for six hours.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:24:05.694 --> 00:24:07.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest we take a break.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:24:07.821 --> 00:24:09.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't argue with that.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:24:09.239 --> 00:24:11.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to my quarters in half an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:24:11.533 --> 00:24:13.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll resume your neuro-pressure regimen.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:24:13.577 --> 00:24:14.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:24:15.036 --> 00:24:17.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd prefer you were rested</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before we make another attempt.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:24:41.980 --> 00:24:43.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I help you?</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:24:45.358 --> 00:24:47.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The captain said it was all right</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if I left my quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:24:47.944 --> 00:24:50.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm Rajiin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I know.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:24:50.947 --> 00:24:52.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>News travels fast on a starship.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:24:52.908 --> 00:24:54.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Ensign Hoshi Sato.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:24:56.119 --> 00:24:57.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a pleasure to meet you.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:25:00.498 --> 00:25:03.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was looking for the mess hall.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:25:04.753 --> 00:25:07.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just happen to be going that way.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:25:12.427 --> 00:25:14.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's your job here?</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:25:14.888 --> 00:25:17.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the ship's communications officer.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:25:17.849 --> 00:25:19.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:25:21.811 --> 00:25:23.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd love to hear your language.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:25:29.277 --> 00:25:32.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I speak quite a few.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:25:53.134 --> 00:25:54.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must be T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:26:03.979 --> 00:26:07.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to startle you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My name is Rajiin.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:26:07.983 --> 00:26:09.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know who you are.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:26:10.360 --> 00:26:12.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:26:12.779 --> 00:26:14.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your door was unlocked.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:26:15.407 --> 00:26:16.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not likely.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:26:17.534 --> 00:26:20.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping we'd have a chance to talk.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:26:21.079 --> 00:26:24.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you are unfamiliar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with our protocols,</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:26:24.165 --> 00:26:28.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it is unacceptable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for you to be in my quarters uninvited.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:26:28.420 --> 00:26:30.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think you'd mind.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:26:32.090 --> 00:26:34.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm afraid--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You're a Vulcan.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:26:34.634 --> 00:26:36.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On a ship filled with humans.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:26:37.012 --> 00:26:38.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:26:40.181 --> 00:26:42.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vulcans and humans are allies.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:26:45.145 --> 00:26:46.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now please leave.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:26:49.399 --> 00:26:52.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't resist.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:26:54.070 --> 00:26:55.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need you to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:26:58.033 --> 00:27:00.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have a disciplined mind.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:27:00.577 --> 00:27:03.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're in such control of your emotions.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:27:04.247 --> 00:27:05.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispers ) Try to let go.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:27:06.583 --> 00:27:08.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighing deeply )</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:27:09.127 --> 00:27:10.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Better.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:27:16.926 --> 00:27:19.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( breathes deeply )</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:27:26.686 --> 00:27:28.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:27:28.938 --> 00:27:30.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let go.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:27:37.655 --> 00:27:38.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:27:45.205 --> 00:27:46.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:27:47.957 --> 00:27:49.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:27:49.209 --> 00:27:51.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:27:53.088 --> 00:27:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:27:59.594 --> 00:28:01.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:28:01.137 --> 00:28:02.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No!</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:28:03.932 --> 00:28:05.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Tucker to the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:28:05.683 --> 00:28:06.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

394
00:28:06.893 --> 00:28:09.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could you tell me where T'Pol is?</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:28:09.270 --> 00:28:11.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>She's in her quarters, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

396
00:28:14.401 --> 00:28:16.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:28:25.662 --> 00:28:26.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:28:36.297 --> 00:28:39.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Tucker to Security.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:28:41.136 --> 00:28:43.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I need assistance.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALE REPTILIAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Were you successful?</i></c.bg_transparent>

400
00:28:43.471 --> 00:28:46.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have what you want.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can use their transporter device,</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:28:46.641 --> 00:28:49.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you'll need to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>within 10,000 kilometers.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:28:49.102 --> 00:28:50.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE REPTILIAN:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Signal us when you're ready.</i></c.bg_transparent>

403
00:28:55.316 --> 00:28:57.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there something wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:28:57.485 --> 00:28:59.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The captain would like to see you.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:28:59.904 --> 00:29:03.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no need to bother the captain.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:29:03.825 --> 00:29:05.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have my orders.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:29:05.744 --> 00:29:06.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do I.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:29:06.953 --> 00:29:08.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:29:41.654 --> 00:29:43.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:29:50.914 --> 00:29:52.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:30:23.780 --> 00:30:25.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you in range?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:30:26.366 --> 00:30:27.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Respond!</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:30:29.452 --> 00:30:31.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leaving so soon?</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:30:38.294 --> 00:30:40.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We jammed your signal.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:30:40.129 --> 00:30:41.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your friends can't hear you.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:30:43.424 --> 00:30:45.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are they?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:30:54.269 --> 00:30:55.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her to the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:31:02.193 --> 00:31:04.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should let me run a neuro-scan.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:31:04.195 --> 00:31:05.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:31:06.072 --> 00:31:07.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to her?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:31:07.740 --> 00:31:09.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't even begin to speculate.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:31:09.784 --> 00:31:12.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's suffered disruptions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>throughout her neocortex.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:31:12.161 --> 00:31:14.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If she were human,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or Denobulan for that matter,</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:31:14.539 --> 00:31:15.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>she'd probably be dead.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:31:15.915 --> 00:31:20.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Vulcan neurophysiology</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is a great deal more resilient than ours.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:31:20.628 --> 00:31:22.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to talk to her.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:31:22.171 --> 00:31:24.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to finish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>treating her injuries first.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:31:24.757 --> 00:31:27.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How long?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-A few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:31:36.728 --> 00:31:38.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have Phlox take a look at your head.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:31:51.534 --> 00:31:52.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beep )</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:31:54.996 --> 00:31:57.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who were you trying to contact?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:31:57.332 --> 00:31:58.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:31:58.708 --> 00:32:01.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I asked you a question.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't answer it.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:32:05.173 --> 00:32:06.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did you do to T'Pol?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:32:06.799 --> 00:32:08.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She shouldn't have resisted.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:32:10.970 --> 00:32:12.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:32:12.472 --> 00:32:15.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you. My name is Rajiin.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:32:15.516 --> 00:32:17.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:32:17.435 --> 00:32:20.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kidnapped when you were a child,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sold into a life of slavery.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:32:21.898 --> 00:32:24.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it was just a coincidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you happened to escape</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:32:24.651 --> 00:32:26.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I was at that market.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:32:28.279 --> 00:32:30.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The chemist knew I was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>looking for information about the Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:32:30.907 --> 00:32:33.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that why you showed up so conveniently?</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:32:34.577 --> 00:32:38.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only thing I can tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is that you're in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:32:38.122 --> 00:32:40.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Care to be a little more specific?</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:32:41.209 --> 00:32:44.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I say anything else, they'll kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:32:46.005 --> 00:32:48.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who? The Xindi?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:32:51.552 --> 00:32:53.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know I won't do the same?</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:32:59.310 --> 00:33:01.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's true that I deceived you.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:33:02.981 --> 00:33:06.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that didn't make your decision</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help me any less admirable.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:33:07.276 --> 00:33:09.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to see you harmed, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:33:11.072 --> 00:33:14.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The best thing for you to do is let me go.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:33:16.285 --> 00:33:18.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me who you contacted.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:33:19.956 --> 00:33:20.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who?</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:33:22.333 --> 00:33:24.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( intercom beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to Captain Archer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

456
00:33:32.218 --> 00:33:33.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:33:33.553 --> 00:33:36.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Two vessels</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>are approaching from aft.</i></c.bg_transparent>

458
00:33:36.431 --> 00:33:38.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, the bio-signs</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>match the genetic profile</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:33:38.307 --> 00:33:40.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of the Xindi pilot who attacked Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:33:40.977 --> 00:33:43.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull plating to full power,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>stand by weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:33:46.607 --> 00:33:48.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The reptilian species.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:33:49.235 --> 00:33:51.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're the ones who sent you.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:33:54.282 --> 00:33:56.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:34:08.296 --> 00:34:09.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:34:09.672 --> 00:34:11.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're dropping out of warp.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:34:22.810 --> 00:34:25.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assume they're here for you.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:34:27.857 --> 00:34:31.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They won't harm anyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you let me go.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:34:31.527 --> 00:34:33.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me if I don't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>take your word on that,</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:34:34.030 --> 00:34:37.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but they murdered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seven million people on my planet.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:34:37.366 --> 00:34:39.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( intercom beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to the captain.</i></c.bg_transparent>

471
00:34:40.828 --> 00:34:42.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:34:42.497 --> 00:34:44.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The smaller ship is approaching</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the starboard docking port.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:34:45.041 --> 00:34:47.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seal that airlock and post security teams.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:34:47.085 --> 00:34:48.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm on my way.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:34:52.882 --> 00:34:54.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was your mission?</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:35:00.973 --> 00:35:04.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-They wanted information.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-About what?</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:35:06.145 --> 00:35:07.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About you.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:35:09.315 --> 00:35:10.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're building a weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:35:10.983 --> 00:35:12.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We know that.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:35:13.653 --> 00:35:15.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is different.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:35:15.446 --> 00:35:16.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A bio-weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:35:18.908 --> 00:35:20.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:35:21.285 --> 00:35:25.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They need data about your species</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before they can begin.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:35:25.957 --> 00:35:27.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where are they building the weapon?</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:35:27.875 --> 00:35:29.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:35:29.627 --> 00:35:32.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-When will it be ready?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:35:37.301 --> 00:35:39.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't tell me anything else.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:35:41.556 --> 00:35:43.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get a security detail down here.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:35:44.642 --> 00:35:46.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's taking her anywhere.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:36:16.007 --> 00:36:17.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fall back!</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:36:23.723 --> 00:36:25.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:36:25.850 --> 00:36:27.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:36:45.536 --> 00:36:48.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three boarding parties,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at least five men each.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:36:48.414 --> 00:36:49.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're headin' for the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:36:49.832 --> 00:36:51.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to cut 'em off.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:36:52.543 --> 00:36:54.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're with me.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:37:09.227 --> 00:37:11.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:37:38.464 --> 00:37:40.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( all groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:37:47.807 --> 00:37:48.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rattling )</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:37:48.933 --> 00:37:50.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapon fires )</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:37:52.853 --> 00:37:55.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( high-pitched beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:38:18.838 --> 00:38:20.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:38:35.187 --> 00:38:36.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:38:43.821 --> 00:38:45.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:38:47.199 --> 00:38:48.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:38:48.826 --> 00:38:51.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:38:52.330 --> 00:38:54.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Archer to the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-TRAVIS: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

508
00:38:54.790 --> 00:38:57.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't let those ships get away!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lay in a pursuit course.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:38:57.168 --> 00:38:58.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:39:10.806 --> 00:39:12.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's dead, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:39:12.558 --> 00:39:14.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( intercom beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:39:14.101 --> 00:39:17.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Those ships just entered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some kind of vortex.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:39:17.229 --> 00:39:18.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:39:18.314 --> 00:39:19.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're gone.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:39:19.607 --> 00:39:21.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:39:29.283 --> 00:39:32.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This gland released</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a fatal dose of neuro-toxin</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:39:32.370 --> 00:39:34.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>into his bloodstream.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:39:34.205 --> 00:39:36.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What kind of species is born</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a suicide gland?</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:39:36.999 --> 00:39:42.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not this one. He was surgically enhanced,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you can call it an enhancement.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:39:42.129 --> 00:39:44.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want a complete autopsy, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:39:44.965 --> 00:39:48.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And have Malcolm take this weapon apart.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:39:48.177 --> 00:39:50.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to find out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>its range, power output,</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:39:50.554 --> 00:39:52.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and how we can defend against it.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:39:52.598 --> 00:39:53.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:39:57.520 --> 00:39:58.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you OK?</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:39:59.647 --> 00:40:00.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:40:01.065 --> 00:40:02.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:40:02.108 --> 00:40:05.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I want an analysis</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the scans we took of those Xindi ships</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:40:05.986 --> 00:40:08.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and find out what you can</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about that vortex they went through.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:40:08.447 --> 00:40:11.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want them dropping in</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>unannounced again.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:40:11.325 --> 00:40:12.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dismissed.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:40:21.877 --> 00:40:24.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've put all of our work at risk.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:40:24.755 --> 00:40:27.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And exposed us to the humans.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:40:27.216 --> 00:40:29.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allowed one of your soldiers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be captured.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:40:29.510 --> 00:40:31.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah! He wasn't taken alive.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:40:31.470 --> 00:40:33.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You agreed to give me more time.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:40:34.432 --> 00:40:37.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't have enough data</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to construct the bio-weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:40:38.060 --> 00:40:39.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't we?</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:40:41.981 --> 00:40:43.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring her!</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:40:43.315 --> 00:40:44.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( footsteps approaching )</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:40:51.907 --> 00:40:53.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Show them.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:40:57.204 --> 00:40:58.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Show them!</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:41:12.803 --> 00:41:15.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We couldn't pursue the bio-weapon</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:41:15.222 --> 00:41:20.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because we didn't have enough information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the humans.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:41:22.813 --> 00:41:24.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now we do.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:41:24.690 --> 00:41:27.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:41:28.027 --> 00:41:32.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you expect us to reward you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for this act of insubordination?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:41:34.074 --> 00:41:37.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This has left us more vulnerable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than we were before.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:41:37.411 --> 00:41:38.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's more to these humans</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:41:38.996 --> 00:41:41.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>than you can learn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from a set of biometric scans.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:41:41.248 --> 00:41:42.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's enough!</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:41:43.792 --> 00:41:44.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her.</c.bg_transparent>

